title: MisterMusic Show 327-New indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 327 - [192 kbps MP3] 2 hours-


New music on this week's show from Thurston Moore, Hey Rosetta,
The Charlatans, and Close Talker. 
The ''Oldie of the Week'' is a big pop song that topped the charts in the US and Canada the end of October 1978.


It's 2 hours of new indie, alternative, and rock mixed with over 5 decades of classic hits-the way radio should be.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on the web on Rock XS radio.


MisterMusic's podcasts can be downloaded or streamed at mistermusicshow.com
